6. If you initialize a Date class object in a singleton, will the Date object be singleton too?
No. Singleton means only one instance of the Singleton class exists. But the DateÂ object inside it is a separate object. Unless you restrict it, DateÂ can be mutable and changed.



7. What design pattern is used with async data update between different clients?
Observer Pattern (Pub-Sub):Â Clients subscribe to updates; when data changes, all subscribers get notified asynchronously.



